	Why not spice things up with a mix of cardamom, creamy bananas and peach? This fantastic blend contains sandalwood and patchouli essential oils that leads to a floral explosion and finishes with warm deep notes of leather, vanilla and musk. This candle will give you hours of burning time to enjoy the beautiful fragrance. When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended. This candle is suitable for vegans.</p>
